WEBVTT

00:15:58.478 --> 00:16:00.100
in the GDP?"

00:16:02.187 --> 00:16:06.353
There's a very important
moral and ethical answer to that,

00:16:07.551 --> 00:16:12.472
and it is that I do not want
the most valuable things on earth,

00:16:12.496 --> 00:16:14.290
the things I treasure,

00:16:14.314 --> 00:16:18.947
sitting in an accounting framework
that thinks that war is great for growth.

00:16:19.463 --> 00:16:24.094
(Applause and cheers)

00:16:28.653 --> 00:16:29.890
